data.eml:eml: New data on the taxonomy, morphology and distribution of Naardaineffectalis (Walker, 1859) (Lepidoptera, Erebidae, Hypeninae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Toth, Balazs (2018): New data on the taxonomy, morphology and distribution of Naardaineffectalis (Walker, 1859) (Lepidoptera, Erebidae, Hypeninae). Nota Lepidopterologica 41 (1): 99-106, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.41.21584, URL: http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/nl.41.21584
